  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This assessment evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across all 13 credibility factors. Seven factors are fully assessed; six are flagged as epistemic gaps consistent with MRL 5. All assessed factors achieve their required gradation levels under this Minimal-profile package. Decision: Accepted.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-req",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-prediction",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/cfd-hemolysis-centrifugal-pump",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-experimental-hemolysis",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/cfd-simulation-outputs-vad"
  ],
